<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTESamuel2010-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTESamuel2010_6-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFSamuel2010">Samuel 2010</a>.</span>
