<li id="cite_note-gflood-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-gflood_8-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Gavin Flood (1996), <i>An Introduction to Hinduism</i>, Cambridge University Press, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0521438780" title="Special:BookSources/978-0521438780">978-0521438780</a>, pp. 35–39</span>
